        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Evippa rajasthanea Tikader & Malhotra, 1980. A–C allotype male left pedipalp (NZC-ZSI-4650/18):A ventral; B ventral enlarged; C retrolateral enlarged. D holotype epigynum without clearing (NZC-ZSI-4648/18), ventral. E–F genitalia of paratype female (NZC-ZSI-4649/18): E epigynum, ventral; F vulva, dorsal. Arrows indicate short disto-lateral processes. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B–F, 0.2 mm." ;
